\alpha_1,\cdots,\alpha_s,\alpha_{s+1}
\beta_i=\alpha_i+t_i\alpha_{s+1},\ i=1,2,\cdots,s
\beta_1,\cdots,\beta_s
\alpha_1,\cdots,\alpha_s,\alpha_{s+1}
\alpha_{s+1} = \frac{\beta_{s+1}}{1+t_{s+1}}
a_{1}\alpha_{1} + ... + a_{s+1}\alpha_{s+1} = 0
a_{1}\left(\beta_{1}-t_{1}\frac{\beta_{s+1}}{1+t_{s+1}}\right) + ... + a_{s+1}\frac{\beta_{s+1}}{1+t_{s+1}} = 0
a_{1} = a_{2} = ... = a_{s+1} = 0
